data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Light and bright, move in ready house with three bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms all on one level. Formal living room, family room with gas fireplace and dining room. The kitchen comes with a gas cooktop, wall oven, skylight, refrigerator and a view to the deck and backyard. Spacious hall laundry closet. Three bay garage with one bay set up at a shop area. Shelving in the garage is great for storage.  Outside you will find a low maintenance landscape all setting on a .33 acre lot. Access to I-5 North or South.
